# =>     в”‚          в”‚                          в”‚                   в”‚ l.com                     в”‚
# =>  16 в”‚ 10ceac99 в”‚ menu keybindings in      в”‚ Fernando Herrera  в”‚ fernando.j.herrera@gmai   в”‚ 2 days ago
# =>     в”‚          в”‚ default file (#4651)     в”‚                   в”‚ l.com                     в”‚
# =>  17 в”‚ 446c2aab в”‚ Lets internals also      в”‚ Sophia            в”‚ 547158+sophiajt@users.nor в”‚ 2 days ago
# =>     в”‚          в”‚ have exit codes (#4664)  в”‚                   в”‚ eply.github.com           в”‚
